data.description: This exquisite home is located in Bridgewater, a beautiful maintenance-free community located right in the heart of Lakewood Ranch. The house features 4 bedrooms, 3.5 baths, a den, high ceilings, crown molding, a kitchen, kitchenette on the second floor, and an outdoor kitchen & grill!  The spacious living room is perfect for relaxing with family and friends. Adjacent to the living room, the kitchen sports granite countertops, a gas stove with hood, built-in stainless steel oven and microwave, sleek wood cabinets, a wine refrigerator, and a breakfast bar! A relaxing master suite, complete with walk-in shower and soaking tub, is on the north side of the split floor plan, ensuring a quiet and restful experience. And finally, with a relaxing heated spa, clear water pool, and outdoor speakers, the lanai is perfect for entertaining that boasts a stunning view of the waterfront behind it!
